Compile: make

Testing socket:
    run ./bin/test_server
    run ./bin/test_client

    Server output:
    ```
        Creating server on 0.0.0.0:8080
        Server started. Waiting for client data...
        Got Hello
        Sent back: ok
        Closing server socket...
    ```

    Client output:
    ```
        Connecting client to 127.0.0.1:8080
        Client sending: Hello
        Message sent. Client waiting for response..
        Client received: ok
    ```